title UC-06: Dropout Risk Identification (Activity)

|Program Manager (Education)|
start
:Login to SCP;
if (Authenticated?) then (no)
  stop
endif

:Select "Education" Vertical;
if (Scope: Vertical "Education"?) then (no)
  :Access Denied (Scope Violation);
  stop
endif

|Vertical: Education|
:Flag < 80% Attendance;

